'''荣耀30系列'''（{{lang-en|HONOR 30 Series}}）是前[[华为|华为]]子公司[[荣耀|荣耀]]于2020年4月15日发布的旗舰手机系列，包括'''荣耀30'''，'''荣耀30 Pro'''以及'''荣耀30 Pro+'''三款手机，並采用左上角挖孔的全面屏设计。Pro系列搭载麒麟990 5G芯片，而标配版搭载麒麟985芯片。

==设计==
荣耀30系列正面采用全面屏，其中荣耀30采用左上角单挖孔全面屏<ref>{{cite web |title=HONOR 30 Price/Specs/Review {{!}} HONOR Official Site (Global) |url=https://www.hihonor.com/global/products/smartphone/honor-30/ |website=www.hihonor.com |accessdate=2020-11-15 |language=en |archive-date=2021-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428235629/https://www.hihonor.com/global/products/smartphone/honor-30/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而荣耀30 Pro系列因为搭载前置双摄而采用了左上角双挖孔全面屏的设计<ref>{{cite web |title=HONOR 30 Pro+ Price/Specs/Review {{!}} HONOR Official Site (Global) |url=https://www.hihonor.com/global/products/smartphone/honor-30-pro-plus/ |website=www.hihonor.com |accessdate=2020-11-15 |language=en |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317161645/https://www.hihonor.com/global/products/smartphone/honor-30-pro-plus/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。背面均采用矩阵式摄像头设计，共有5种配色，分别为钛空银（Titanium Silver）、霓影紫（Neon Purple）、幻夜黑（Midnight Black）、绿野仙踪（Emerald Green）、流光幻境（Icelandic Frost）。其中钛空银配色背面采用AG磨砂玻璃工艺<ref>{{cite web |title=Honor 30 and 30 Pro get a new color option |url=https://www.gsmarena.com/honor_30_and_30_pro_get_new_color_option_in_china-news-43291.php |website=GSMArena.com |accessdate=2020-11-15 |archive-date=2020-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921083904/https://www.gsmarena.com/honor_30_and_30_pro_get_new_color_option_in_china-news-43291.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>，钛空银及霓影紫两种配色背面的荣耀“HONOR”標誌亦被横置放大以凸显不同<ref>{{cite web |last1=Petrova |first1=Iskra |title=Honor 30 Pro Plus Review |url=https://www.phonearena.com/reviews/Honor-30-Pro-Plus-Review_id4822 |website=Phone Arena |accessdate=2020-11-15 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227165543/https://www.phonearena.com/reviews/Honor-30-Pro-Plus-Review_id4822 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

荣耀30 Pro系列的屏幕为70°“飞瀑屏”<ref>{{cite web |title=荣耀30 Pro产品介绍_荣耀30 Pro功能_荣耀30 Pro产品特性-荣耀官网 |url=https://www.honor.cn/products/mobile-phones/honor30pro/ |website=www.honor.cn |accessdate=2020-11-15 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126062002/https://www.honor.cn/products/mobile-phones/honor30pro/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，荣耀30的屏幕则是非曲面屏，全系列均保留了实体音量按键。荣耀30 Pro系列均支持[[国际防护等级认证|IP54]]防水防尘<ref>{{cite web |title=荣耀30 Pro+参数_荣耀30 Pro+配置_荣耀30 Pro+规格性能-荣耀官网 |url=https://www.honor.cn/products/mobile-phones/honor30-pro/spec/ |website=www.honor.cn |accessdate=2020-11-15 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126011547/https://www.honor.cn/products/mobile-phones/honor30-pro/spec/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==性能与体验==
荣耀30 Pro系列搭载[[海思|麒麟990 5G]]芯片，而荣耀30则搭载[[海思|麒麟985]]芯片<ref>{{cite web |title=Honor 30's Kirin 985 chipset gets benchmarked, scores slightly better than the Kirin 820 |url=https://www.gsmarena.com/honor_30s_kirin_985_chipset_gets_benchmarked_scores_slightly_better_than_the_kirin_820-news-42690.php |website=GSMArena.com |accessdate=2020-11-15 |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115074142/https://www.gsmarena.com/honor_30s_kirin_985_chipset_gets_benchmarked_scores_slightly_better_than_the_kirin_820-news-42690.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

搭载在荣耀30上的麒麟985 5G芯片是第一次发布，基于[[台灣積體電路製造|台积电]]7nm工艺制造<ref>{{cite web |last1=Ikoba |first1=Jed John |title=Kirin 985 announced: 7nm process, 5G performance upgrade & more! |url=https://www.gizmochina.com/2020/04/15/huawei-kirin-985-7nm-process-5g-performance-upgrade/ |website=Gizmochina |accessdate=2020-11-15 |date=2020-04-15 |archive-date=2020-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218073421/https://www.gizmochina.com/2020/04/15/huawei-kirin-985-7nm-process-5g-performance-upgrade/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，搭载基于[[ARM_Cortex-A76|ARM Cortex-A76]]与[[ARM_Cortex-A55|ARM Cortex-A55]]的8核CPU以及[[Mali_(GPU)|Mali-G77]]GPU<ref>{{cite web |last1=Frumusanu |first1=Andrei |title=Honor Launches Honor 30 Series in China: Three New Premium Devices |url=https://www.anandtech.com/show/15722/honor-launches-honor-30-series-in-china-three-new-premium-devices |website=www.anandtech.com |accessdate=2020-11-15 |archive-date=2021-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301080420/https://www.anandtech.com/show/15722/honor-launches-honor-30-series-in-china-three-new-premium-devices |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而荣耀30 Pro系列上则搭载麒麟990 5G芯片，该SoC曾在[[华为Mate_30系列|华为Mate 30系列]]、[[华为P40|华为P40]]、[[华为Mate_Xs|华为Mate Xs]]等机型中搭载。

荣耀30系列搭载OLED屏幕，而荣耀30 Pro+搭载了支持90Hz刷新率的OLED屏幕<ref>{{cite web |author1=João Carrasqueira |title=Honor 30 Pro+ unboxing and first impressions |url=https://www.neowin.net/news/honor-30-pro-unboxing-and-first-impressions/ |website=neowin.net |accessdate=2020-11-15 |archive-date=2021-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315201654/https://www.neowin.net/news/honor-30-pro-unboxing-and-first-impressions/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，全系均支持光学屏下指纹及NFC。

==摄像==
===后置相机===
荣耀30搭载了四颗摄像头，而荣耀30 Pro系列搭载了三颗摄像头。

荣耀30与荣耀30 Pro的主摄均为4000万像素IMX600超感光摄像头<ref>{{cite web |title=Photos taken with camera of Huawei Honor 30 |url=https://www.kimovil.com/en/huawei-honor-30/camera |website=Kimovil.com |accessdate=2020-11-15 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116183256/https://www.kimovil.com/en/huawei-honor-30/camera |dead-url=no }}</ref>，该摄像头亦曾在华为Mate 30系列上被搭载，而在荣耀30 Pro+上，主摄被替换成了5000万像素IMX700超感光摄像头<ref>{{cite web |title=HONOR 30 Flagship Appears With 50MP Sony IMX700 Camera & More |url=https://www.androidheadlines.com/2020/04/honor-30-50mp-camera-leak.html |website=Android Headlines |accessdate=2020-11-15 |date=2020-04-03 |archive-date=2020-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200406115024/https://www.androidheadlines.com/2020/04/honor-30-50mp-camera-leak.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，该摄像头与华为P40主摄相同<ref>{{cite web |last1=Ogbonyenitan |first1=Gbenga |title=Honor 30, Honor 30 Pro, and Honor 30 Pro+: Features, Reviews, and Prices |url=https://www.techidence.com/honor-30-honor-30-pro-and-honor-30-pro-features-reviews-and-prices/ |website=Techidence |accessdate=2020-11-15 |date=2020-04-15 |archive-date=2021-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224175529/https://www.techidence.com/honor-30-honor-30-pro-and-honor-30-pro-features-reviews-and-prices/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

除此之外，荣耀30系列均搭载了800万像素潜望长焦式镜头，支持5倍光学变焦与最大50倍变焦<ref>{{cite web |title=Honor 30 series goes live with great cameras but no Google services |url=https://www.androidcentral.com/honor-30-series-goes-live-50x-zoom-camera-atrocious-branding |website=Android Central |accessdate=2020-11-15 |date=2020-04-15 |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123025152/https://www.androidcentral.com/honor-30-series-goes-live-50x-zoom-camera-atrocious-branding |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

荣耀30 Pro+后置相机在[[DXOMARK|DXOMARK]]评分中获得了125分<ref>{{cite web |title=Honor 30 Pro+ camera review |url=https://www.dxomark.com/honor-30-pro-plus-camera-review/ |website=DXOMARK |accessdate=2020-11-15 |date=2020-04-15 |archive-date=2021-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210509130003/https://www.dxomark.com/honor-30-pro-plus-camera-review/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===前置相机===
荣耀30系列前置主摄均搭载3200万像素单摄，而荣耀30 Pro系列还另外增加了一颗800万像素摄像头<ref>{{cite web |title=Honor 30 Pro Plus review: Forget the Huawei P40, buy this instead (if you can) |url=https://www.androidauthority.com/honor-30-pro-plus-review-1132836/ |website=Android Authority |accessdate=2020-11-15 |date=2020-09-01 |archive-date=2021-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228115704/https://www.androidauthority.com/honor-30-pro-plus-review-1132836/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==续航==
荣耀30系列均搭载4000毫安时电池<ref>{{cite web |title=Honor 30, Honor 30 Pro, Honor 30 Pro+ With 4,000mAh Battery Launched |url=https://gadgets.ndtv.com/mobiles/news/honor-30-pro-plus-price-cny-2999-launch-specifications-features-2212324 |website=NDTV Gadgets 360 |accessdate=2020-11-15 |language=en |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116150919/https://gadgets.ndtv.com/mobiles/news/honor-30-pro-plus-price-cny-2999-launch-specifications-features-2212324 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并均支持40W有线快充，而荣耀30 Pro+则支持27W无线快充<ref>{{cite web |last1=Joseph |first1=Joel |title=Honor 30, Honor 30 Pro, & Pro+ launched with Kirin 990, 40W Charging & Periscope Cameras |url=https://www.gizmochina.com/2020/04/15/honor-30-honor-30-pro-pro-launched-with-kirin-990-40w-charging-periscope-cameras/ |website=Gizmochina |accessdate=2020-11-15 |date=2020-04-15 |archive-date=2020-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118223737/https://www.gizmochina.com/2020/04/15/honor-30-honor-30-pro-pro-launched-with-kirin-990-40w-charging-periscope-cameras/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==软件==
荣耀30系列搭载基于[[Android_10|Android 10]]的Magic UI 3.1.1。

由于[[美國對中華人民共和國的制裁|美国制裁]]，荣耀30系列不支持[[Google_Play服務|Google Play服務]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Honor 30 Pro+ review: An incredible camera, but Android without Google doesn't cut it |url=https://www.neowin.net/news/honor-30-pro-review-an-incredible-camera-but-android-without-google-doesnt-cut-it/ |website=Neowin |accessdate=2020-11-15 |language=en |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125181428/https://www.neowin.net/news/honor-30-pro-review-an-incredible-camera-but-android-without-google-doesnt-cut-it |dead-url=no }}</ref>，无法在中国大陆以外使用[[Gmail|Gmail]]、[[Google_地图|Google 地图]]等依赖GMS服务的应用。

